        JsonArray polling(String deviceType, String deviceId, String SensorType) throws ParseException

        Poll the server until obtain the last state of a device's sensor. If polling is to long, then stop.

        Parameters:
        deviceType - - The device's type
        deviceId - - The device's Id
        SensorType - - The sensor's type
        Returns:
        A JsonArray if last state is found, empty JsonArray otherwise..

        java.text.ParseException
